# ShredOS

This repository contains the Buildroot-based source tree for ShredOS, a small
bootable operating system for securely erasing disks with nwipe.

Start with README.md for the project documentation:

  - downloads and release notes
  - writing ShredOS to USB, CD/DVD, or Ventoy media
  - nwipe configuration, certificates, logs, and headless operation
  - building ShredOS from source

Buildroot documentation is still available in docs/manual. You can generate the
text manual with:

  make manual-text

The generated manual is written to output/docs/manual/manual.text.
